parameters:
\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Your expression is still stiff... and your
lines need to be more seductive... You
should know what kind of scene it is,
right?

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Your expression has improved♪ But
unfortunately, your lines lack
emotion...

\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]I've been stumbling in the 'playful
mischief' scene since earlier.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Hmm... Since Reiko is a sexually liberated
person, you need to act based on that,
you know?

\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]Regardless of being out of my field, since I
accepted this as a job, I can't afford
to do it half-heartedly.

\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]...However, the more I try to take it seriously and
work on it, the more I get stuck in a
quagmire without knowing the right
answer.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Don't worry... there's no need to rush, you
know? That's why we're having these
private lessons, hehe~?

Udo, the director, who said that, stood up
and approached the clumsy actress in
front of him, placing his hand on her
shoulder.

\n<Udo>It seems like it would be better for Neon-
chan to start getting used to men, don't
you think?
